91bea7136a89b2bef6439f019aaa3b7c2b53f868.text_content: GnuCash Android supports working with multiple different Books (ledgers) simultaneously.
However, only the accounts and transactions of one book displayed at any given time. But you can switch easily between different books.
In order to switch books do the following:
Open the navigation drawer (by tapping the Hamburger menu at top left)
Below the name of the app, you will see the name of the currently active book. Tap on it
The recently used books will be displayed. Select any one to open it
If the book you want is not displayed, selece "Manage Books"
A list of all books currently in the app will be displayed. Select any one to load it
Now you can mix business and pleasure while keeping them separate ;)
